      in Klebsiella pneumoniae, especially the hypervirulent bla(KPC)-positive
      K. pneumoniae (Hv-bla(KPC)(+)-KP). METHODS: A total of 521 complete
      genomes of K. pneumoniae from GenBank were collected and analyzed.
