      had functional conjugation-associated genes and was transferable to
      Escherichia coli. CONCLUSION: pKAM260_2, the self-transmissible plasmid
      carrying thebla(KPC-2) gene, was detected from hospital sewage water in
      Japan and was characterised as a pKpQIL-like plasmid. This plasmid needs
      to be monitored in Japan in the future owing to its high diffusivity.
