AB  - The emergence of carbapenem-resistant Klebsiella pneumoniae (CRKP)
      isolates in Egyptian hospitals has been reported. However, the genetic
      basis and analysis of the plasmids associated with carbapenem-resistant
      hypervirulent K. pneumoniae (CR-HvKP) in Egypt have not been presented.
