      model using FK506 in WT C57BL/6 mice. We further demonstrated that
      immunotherapy with recombinant IL-22 treatment ameliorated the ST258
      pulmonary infection in both FK506-treated WT mice and Rag2-/- Il2rg-/-
      mice via hepatic IL-22ra1 signaling. These data support the development of
      host-directed immunotherapy as an adjunct treatment to new antibiotics.
