      compared the bactericidal activity of meropenem innovator (AstraZeneca)
      and four generic products (Actavis, Kabi, Mylan and Panpharma), both in
      vitro and in vivo, in association with colistin. In vitro time-kill
      studies were performed at 4 × MIC. An experimental model of KPC-producing
