      to ST11. Three strains were isolated from the same patient; each carried a
      different plasmid replicon, either IncFII ((pHN7A8)), IncX, or IncFIB
      ((K)). CONCLUSION: This study furthers the understanding of CRKP
      antimicrobial resistance genotypes, and may facilitate the control of
      nosocomial infections caused by antimicrobial-resistant pathogens.
