      of carbapenemase-producing Enterobacteriaceae (CPE) from 3 tertiary-care
      Korean university hospitals between 2017 and 2018. Non-duplicated clinical
      isolates of Enterobacteriaceae showing resistance to any carbapenem agents
      were collected prospectively from 3 tertiary university hospitals between
