      chromosomal mutations in Two Component Systems(TCS) PhoPQ and PmrAB and
      plasmid-borne genes(mcr and its variants). The aim of this study was to
      understand the molecular basis of colistin resistance in Klebsiella
      pneumoniae and determine clonal transmission, in a North Indian tertiary
