      genes mgrB, phoP, phoQ, pmrA, pmrB were analysed. Sequence typing was
      performed by Multilocus sequence typing(MLST). OXA-48 was detected in
      thirteen isolates while three isolates co-expressed OXA-48 and NDM. The
      mcr-1 gene was absent in all 16 isolates. Deleterious mutations in mgrB
      included insertion sequences IS903 and ISkpn26 and a premature stop codon.
