      which, novel mutations were reported in phoQ (K46E, L322V, D152N, F373L,
      R249G), pmrB (P159R) and pmrA (D149L). Six different sequence types ST231,
      ST147, ST395, ST42, ST14 and ST101 were identified. Phylogenetic analysis
      showed that sequence types ST14, ST395 and ST147 are closely related to
      ST101 and all identified sequence types had a common ancestor ST231.
