      infection and/or colonization of carbapenemase-producing Enterobacterales
      (CPE) based on clinical and microbiological data for patients in the
      intensive care unit (ICU). All patients admitted to medical ICU were
      screened for CPE on admission and weekly, and this 1:2 case-control study
      included patients with CPE identified by screening or clinical cultures
      from 2017 to 2018. The clonal relatedness was evaluated by pulsed-field
