      non-fatal case of peripheral line associated BSI (PLA-BSI) in an
      immunocompromised host due to P. putida harboring blaKPC-2 gene in Brazil.
      A P. putida isolate was recovered from a blood culture of a 72-year-old
      man admitted at a University Hospital, identified by BD Phoenix™ 100
