AB  - Meropenem/vaborbactam (M/V) is a new carbapenem-carbapenemase inhibitor
      combination drug active against extensively drug resistant Gram-negative
      pathogens. Studies about its efficacy and place in therapy are limited in
      "real-life" and no data are available for deep site infections, like
      vascular graft infections. We present a case of a patient successfully
