      demonstrated the remarkable synergism between AS101 and AZT, with the
      observable decrease in the MIC value for two agents and the fractional
      inhibitory concentration (FIC) index ≤0.5 in all strains. Hence, the
      combination of AS101 and azidothymidine could be a potential treatment
      option against CRKP for drug development.
